  "open_questions_for_thony": [
    "1. Sampling frequency: how often should we read sensors? (e.g. every 1s, 2s, 5s)",
    "2. Impact threshold: minimum g_force to trigger an immediate flush (e.g. ≥4g, ≥6g)?",
    "3. IoT node vs phone: will Phase 1.5 use the rider's smartphone only, or a dedicated device?",
    "4. MQTT vs Supabase Realtime: Supabase RT is the current fallback — confirm or specify broker details.",
    "5. Periodic flush interval: currently 15 min — is that the agreed window, or should it be shorter?",
    "6. Fields needed beyond the current schema? (e.g. gyroscope x/y/z, RPM, fuel level from IoT)"
  ]
}
